<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<!--<h4>First Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>śākābdhē śarasū 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>rra rasmi gaṇitērē 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>rāṁbbika naṁdanō gā 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ragrāmanivāsinē 
<lb n="5"/>bhagavatē prādādbhudhā 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>naṁdanaḥ gokanna kuladī 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>paka śśubhatithau dīpammu 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>dā viṣṇavē khaṇḍaṁ brahmasu 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>tōṇḍajādhiphalasatprakhyā 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>taśāryyōraṇē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīmaddē 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>vēṁdravarmmadēvara pravaddha 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>māna vijayarājya saṁva 
<lb n="13" break="no"/>tsaraṁbulu 7 Agunēṁṭi 
<lb n="14"/>dhanumāsamuna nuttarā 
</p>

<!--<h4>Second Face.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="15" break="no"/>rāyeṇa ni 
<lb n="16" break="no"/>mityamu 
<lb n="17" break="no"/>na predda A 
<lb n="18" break="no"/>llu gōka 
<lb n="19" break="no"/>nāyaku 
<lb n="20" break="no"/>ṇḍu gāra 
<lb n="21" break="no"/>nārāyaṇa 
<lb n="22"/>dēvaraku 
<lb n="23"/>Akhaṇḍa 
<lb n="24" break="no"/>varttiki gā 
<lb n="25" break="no"/>rapaiṁbeṭṭina 
<lb n="26"/>Eḍlu 50 
<lb n="27"/>dīnināca 
<lb n="28" break="no"/>ṁdrarkamu na 
<lb n="29" break="no"/>ḍapaṁgala 
<lb n="30" break="no"/>vāru 
</p>

